clocksource/drivers/efm32: Use CLOCK_EVT_FEAT_PERIODIC for defining features

We have used CLOCK_EVT_MODE_PERIODIC instead of
CLOCK_EVT_FEAT_PERIODIC while defining features. Fix it.

